<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>19-308</num>
  <heading>Share of father and mother.</heading>
  <text>When the intestate leaves no child, or descendant, the whole is divided equally between the father and mother or their survivor.</text>
